title: Fuck it I love you
author: Lana Del Rey
lyrics:
[00:00.87] I like to see everything in neon
[00:05.18] Drink lime green, stay up 'til dawn
[00:08.66] Maybe the way that I'm living is killing me
[00:15.60] I like to light up the stage with a song
[00:19.97] Do shit to keep me turned on
[00:23.55] But one day I woke up like
[00:26.09] "Maybe I'll do it differently"
[00:29.04] So I moved to California but it's just a state of mind
[00:32.72] It turns out everywhere you go, you take yourself, that's not a lie
[00:36.63] Wish that you would hold me or just say that you were mine
[00:40.28] It's killing me slowly
[00:45.77] Dream a little dream of me
[00:49.74] Make me into something sweet
[00:53.16] Turn the radio on, dancing to a pop song
[00:57.35] Fuck it, I love you
[01:01.34] Fuck it, I love you
[01:05.11] Fuck it, I love you
[01:08.36] I really do
[01:12.90] 
[01:15.02] I used to shoot up my veins in neon
[01:19.27] And shit's even brighter, you're gone
[01:22.64] So many things I would say to you
[01:26.69] I want you
[01:28.51] You moved to California, but it's just a state of mind
[01:31.85] And you know everyone adores you
[01:33.63] You can't feel it and you're tired
[01:35.71] Baby wish that you would hold me or just say that you were mine
[01:39.46] But it's killing me slowly
[01:45.27] Dream a little dream of me
[01:48.95] Turn this into something sweet

[01:56.88] Fuck it, I love you
[02:00.52] Fuck it, I love you
[02:04.39] Fuck it, I love you
[02:07.83] I really do
[02:12.63] It turns out California's more than just a state of mind
[02:16.27] I met you on the boulevard, wind through my hair, you blew my mind
[02:19.79] And if I wasn't so fucked up, I think I'd fuck you all the time
[02:23.51] (I really do) It's killing me slowly
[02:27.01] Fuck it, I love you (I moved to California, but it's just a state of mind)
[02:30.63] Fuck it, I love you (It turns out everywhere you go, you take yourself, that's not a lie)
[02:34.22] Fuck it, I love you (Wish that you would hold me or just say that you were mine)
[02:38.00] I really do (It's killing me slowly)
[02:41.79] Fuck it, I love you (California dreamin', got my money on my mind)
[02:45.17] Fuck it, I love you (Chances in my veins, running out of time)
[02:48.96] Fuck it, I love you (California dreamin', got my money on my mind)
